            "content_html": "<img src=\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/5368500?v=4\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\" alt=\"\"/><br/><p dir=\"auto\">FF has added support for the Selection.direction and Selection.getComposedRange (as has Safari). This adds docs.</p>\n<p dir=\"auto\">In draft because this is complicated.</p>\n<p dir=\"auto\">Related docs work in: <a class=\"issue-link js-issue-link\" data-error-text=\"Failed to load title\" data-id=\"2253977510\" data-permission-text=\"Title is private\" data-url=\"https://github.com/mdn/content/issues/33180\" data-hovercard-type=\"issue\" data-hovercard-url=\"/mdn/content/issues/33180/hovercard\" href=\"https://github.com/mdn/content/issues/33180\">#33180</a></p>",
